quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,The striking calamity
  101,2,What is the striking calamity
  101,3,And how would you know what is the striking calamity
  101,4,It is the Day when the human beings will be like dispersed moths
  101,5,and the mountains will be like fluffed up wool
  101,6,"and then, the one whose scales are heavy [with good deeds]"
  101,7,will have a pleasant life
  101,8,but the one whose scales are light
  101,9,his refuge will be an abyss
  101,10,And what will convey to you what that is
  101,11,a Raging Fire